00:07:16.290 --> 00:07:24.800
So this is an opposite question. You have
been given the task to find the point on y-axis

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:28.550
such that the perpendicular distance from
the line to the point is unity. So, how will

00:07:28.550 --> 00:07:29.550
